race.comment: SOTOMAYOR (3) is an improving galloper who can build on the Terang placing over this distance. Has been kept on the fresh side and should secure a softish run and this might prove the difference. SUNSET BEAUTY (7) ran his best race beaten a whisker over 1400m at Sale when positioning forward. Has to manage an awkward gate today, but will present at peak fitness and with average luck she can go one better. LA MEETING (13) was plain last time but the form prior reads well for this contest. The inside gate should advantage and he has winning claims. RICKY RUNS (2) didn't enjoy the heavy track at Stony Creek and has been freshened. His form leading into that would see him competitive in this.
